# sinaasappel
Useful utils

## Recursive sum

Use the following commands to calculate the sum of a nested list of ints:

```python
from sinaasappel import recursive_sum

list_sum = recursive_sum([1, 2, [3, [4]]])
print(list_sum)  # prints 10
```


